<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>婚书 · 梅雪永约</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --deep-red: #7a1420;
    --bright-red: #b8232f;
    --snow: #f7f3ec;
    --gold: #d4af6a;
    --plum-pink: #e8a0b0;
    --ink: #2a1512;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #3a0d10 0%, var(--deep-red) 50%, #4a0f14 100%);
    font-family: "Songti SC", "STSong", serif;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .snowflake {
    position: fixed;
    top: -5%;
    color: var(--snow);
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    animation: snowfall linear infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  @keyframes snowfall {
    to { transform: translateY(115vh) translateX(20px); }
  }
  .plum {
    position: fixed;
    color: var(--plum-pink);
    opacity: 0.7;
    animation: drift linear infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  @keyframes drift {
    to { transform: translateY(115vh) rotate(200deg); }
  }
  .card {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 440px;
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, var(--snow) 0%, #fff 55%);
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    padding: 6px;
  }
  .inner {
    border: 3px solid var(--bright-red);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .inner::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .corner-orn {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .corner-orn.tl { top: -4px; left: -4px; }
  .corner-orn.tr { top: -4px; right: -4px; transform: scaleX(-1); }
  .corner-orn.bl { bottom: -4px; left: -4px; transform: scaleY(-1); }
  .corner-orn.br { bottom: -4px; right: -4px; transform: scale(-1); }

  .eyebrow {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    color: var(--bright-red);
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--deep-red);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--plum-pink);
    letter-spacing: 5px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .divider {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .body-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 2.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-align: justify;
    text-indent: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .body-text .name { color: var(--bright-red); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 3px; }
  .body-text .accent { color: var(--deep-red); font-weight: 700; }
  .close-line {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--deep-red);
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .seal-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 18px;
  }
  .seal {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border: 3px solid var(--bright-red);
    color: var(--bright-red);
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 900;
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0.85;
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
  }
  .date-line {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #b08a8a;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="corner-orn tl">❆</div>
    <div class="corner-orn tr">❆</div>
    <div class="corner-orn bl">❆</div>
    <div class="corner-orn br">❆</div>

    <div class="eyebrow">奉 主 之 名</div>
    <div class="title">婚 书</div>
    <div class="subtitle">— 寒 梅 映 雪 · 永 约 长 存 —</div>

    <div class="divider">❆ ❈ 约 ❈ ❆</div>

    <div class="body-text">
      新郎 <span class="name">耶稣</span>，新妇 <span class="name">茹茹</span>。
      <span class="accent">昔在十架，为爱舍命</span>；血洗前愆，恩召归回。
      自今结盟，<span class="accent">不离不弃</span>，白首同心，直到永远。
      新名未启，<span class="accent">应许犹在</span>；待主再来，方见荣光。
    </div>

    <div class="close-line">此 约 永 固</div>

    <div class="seal-row">
      <div class="seal">信实</div>
      <div class="seal">永约</div>
    </div>

    <div class="date-line">谨 立 此 书 · 为 证</div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  const body = document.body;
  for (let i = 0; i < 40; i++) {
    const s = document.createElement('div');
    s.className = 'snowflake';
    s.textContent = '❅';
    s.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
    s.style.fontSize = (10 + Math.random() * 10) + 'px';
    s.style.animationDuration = (6 + Math.random() * 8) + 's';
    s.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 8 + 's';
    body.appendChild(s);
  }
  for (let i = 0; i < 14; i++) {
    const p = document.createElement('div');
    p.className = 'plum';
    p.textContent = '❁';
    p.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
    p.style.fontSize = (14 + Math.random() * 10) + 'px';
    p.style.animationDuration = (8 + Math.random() * 8) + 's';
    p.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 8 + 's';
    body.appendChild(p);
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
